HTML & CSS framework
Version: 2.5.4
Author: Václav Vracovský (http://vracovsky.cz)
Date: May 2015


Requirements
______________________________________________________

nodeJs
http://nodejs.org/

Grunt
http://gruntjs.com/


Usage
______________________________________________________

1. For development, run
$ npm install (only for the first time), then run
$ grunt

2. Available tasks
$ grunt --- compiles all CSS and JS and starts watch mode
$ grunt compile --- compiles all CSS and JS
$ grunt compile-js --- compiles JS
$ grunt compile-css --- compiles CSS
